Package SpaceExplorer

Class Game

  • java.lang.Object
    • SpaceExplorer.Game
  • public class Game
extends java.lang.Object
    Game class used to set up the game and keep track of the other classes used to play. Also calculates player's final score and stores all the items that are possible to obtain in the game.
    Version:
    1.0, May 2019
    Author:
    Saahil Hari and Isaac Walton
